high_descs: Turn around and look down at the dresser.
Pick up the leftmost candle off of the dresser.
Turn around and take two steps forward, then turn left and walk forward, turn left again to face the dresser.
Open the bottom right drawer of the dresser and put the candle inside in the back left corner, then close the drawer.
Walk up to the dresser.
Pick up the candle off of the dresser.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn right and take a step, turn right again to face the dresser.
Open the bottom right drawer of the dresser and put the candle inside to the right of the candle that is already in there, then close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Move two candles into the drawer of a dresser.

high_descs: turn around and look down at the table
pick up the candle off of the table
turn around and walk straight then turn left and walk straight then turn left again and walk straight towards the table
open the drawer on the right side of the table and put the candle inside and close the drawer
turn right and walk straight then turn left and walk towards the table
pick up the candle at the back of the table
turn around and walk straight then turn right then right again and walk straight towards the table
open the drawer and put the candle inside and close the drawer
anns.task_desc: clean up candle's and put them inside the table drawer

high_descs: Turn around to face the white drawers.
Pick up the candlestick on the left.
Walk to the right side of the drawers.
Put the candlestick away in the lower rightmost drawer.
Turn to face the top of the white drawers.
Pick up the candlestick on the right.
Turn to face the lower white drawers.
Put the other candlestick away in the lower rightmost drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put two candlesticks away in a drawer.
